BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 661.50 Tm (When you unzip the project you'll find this layout - standard Maven convention, so every Spring) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 646.50 Tm (Boot project looks familiar once you know it. src-main-java holds your application code, including) Tj ET
